{"title_page": "List of All of Us episodes", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''All of Us'' episodes}}\n''[[All of Us]]'' is an American [[situation comedy|sitcom]] that premiered on [[UPN]] network on September 16, 2003. The series aired on UPN for its first three seasons, airing its final episode on UPN on May 15, 2006. On October 1, 2006, the show moved to [[The CW]], a new network formed by the merger of UPN and [[The WB]], where it aired for fourth and final season; the last episode aired on May 14, 2007, and the series was cancelled by The CW on May 15, 2007.<ref name=\"Variety\">{{cite news |url=https://variety.com/2007/tv/features/cw-picks-up-dramas-1117964957/ |title=CW picks up dramas |author=Adalian, Josef |work=Variety |date=May 15, 2007 |accessdate=2018-08-07}}</ref>  [[Warner Bros. Television]] produced this series. A total of 88 episodes aired over the four seasons.\n\n==Series overview==\n<!-- Full linking is used in the following template because it is transcluded to the main series article -->\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n\n| color1     = #ffb629\n| link1      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 1: 2003\u201304\n| episodes1  = 22\n| start1     = {{Start date|2003|9|16}}\n| end1       = {{End date|2004|5|18}}\n| network1   = [[UPN]]\n\n| color2     = #9c2308\n| link2      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 2: 2004\u201305\n| episodes2  = 22\n| start2     = {{Start date|2004|9|21}}\n| end2       = {{End date|2005|5|24}}\n\n| color3     = 000\n| link3      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 3: 2005\u201306\n| episodes3  = 22\n| start3     = {{Start date|2005|9|19}}\n| end3       = {{End date|2006|5|15}}\n\n| color4     = #E17B3F\n| link4      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 4: 2006\u201307\n| episodes4  = 22\n| start4     = {{Start date|2006|10|1}}\n| end4       = {{End date|2007|5|14}}\