cw-picks-up-dramas-1117964957/ |title=CW picks up dramas |author=Adalian, Josef |work=Variety |date=May 15, 2007 |accessdate=2018-08-07}}</ref>  [[Warner Bros. Television]] produced this series. A total of 88 episode aired over the four seasons.\n\n==Series overview==\n<!-- Full linking is used in the following template because it is transcluded to the main series article -->\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n\n| color1     = #ffb629\n| link1      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 1: 2003\u201304\n| episodes1  = 22\n| start1     = {{Start date|2003|9|16}}\n| end1       = {{End date|2004|5|18}}\n| network1   = [[UPN]]\n\n| color2     = #9c2308\n| link2      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 2: 2004\u201305\n| episodes2  = 22\n| start2     = {{Start date|2004|9|21}}\n| end2       = {{End date|2005|5|24}}\n\n| color3     = 000\n| link3      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 3: 2005\u201306\n| episodes3  = 22\n| start3     = {{Start date|2005|9|19}}\n| end3       = {{End date|2006|5|15}}\n\n| color4     = #E17B3F\n| link4      = <includeonly>List of All of Us episodes</includeonly>#Season 4: 2006\u201307\n| episodes4  = 22\n| start4     = {{Start date|2006|10|1}}\n| end4       = {{End date|2007|5|14}}\n| network4   = [[The CW]]\n\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Episodes==\n===Season 1: 2003\u201304===\n{| class=wikitable style=\"width:95%; background:#FFFFFF\"\n! style=\"background:#ffb629; width:20px\"| {{abbr|N\u00ba|Overall episode number}}\n! style=\"background:#ffb629; width:20px\"| {{abbr|Ep|Episode number by season}}\n! style=\"background:#ffb629\"| Title\n! style=\"background:#ffb629; width:110px\"| Directed by:\n! style=\"background:#ffb629; width:150px\"| Written by:\n! style=\"background:#ffb629; width:135px\"| Original air date\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 1\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n| Title = Pilot\n| DirectedBy = [[Stan Lathan]]\n| WrittenBy = Betsy Borns ({{abbr|s/t|story and 